# Global Export Analysis Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📊 Overview
This project analyzes global export data for a company, focusing on sales, orders, products, and logistics performance. The dashboard provides insights into how different categories, countries, and employees contribute to overall exports.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze export performance across countries and categories
- Track total orders, sales, and product distribution
- Understand employee contribution to exports
- Identify top-performing products and discounted items
- Explore logistics and shipping performance

## 📌 Key Features
- KPI cards showing Total Orders, Sales, Quantity, and Net Amount
- Export analysis by category, country, and company
- Employee-level performance tracking
- Category-wise deep dive (Seafood, Beverages, Dairy, etc.)
- Interactive filters for year, quarter, and month
- Product-level insights including pricing and discounts
- Geographic visualization using map charts

## 🔍 Insights
- Certain countries contribute significantly higher export volumes
- A few product categories dominate total exports
- Employee performance varies widely across regions
- Discounted products show higher sales concentration
- Logistics (freight and shipping companies) impact overall distribution efficiency

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data Modeling
- Interactive Dashboard Design

## 📁 Files
- Export_Analysis.pbix
- Export_Analysis.pdf

